  "title": "Simple circuits - Bulb 1 off and Bulb 2 on",
  "content": {
    "prompt": "<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows a rectangular circuit diagram with a battery, two bulbs labeled Bulb 1 and Bulb 2, and two switches labeled Switch 1 and Switch 2. The circuit has three vertical branches and two horizontal branches. The left vertical branch has the battery. The middle vertical branch has Bulb 1. The right vertical branch has Bulb 2. From left to right, the top horizontal branch has Switch 1 between the left and middle vertical branches, and has Switch 2 between the middle and right vertical branches.\" src=\"/images/afc1ac3340644392e4ddbc3f8243a4df.svg\"></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">A circuit is comprised of a battery, two bulbs, and two switches, as shown in the figure. What combination of switch positions, if any, would result in Bulb <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1\"><math alttext=\"1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span> being off and Bulb <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn></math></span></span> being on?</p>\n",
    "answer": "i4",
    "choices": [
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Both switches closed</p>",
        "value": "i1"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Switch <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1\"><math alttext=\"1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span> closed and Switch <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn></math></span></span> open</p>",
        "value": "i2"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Switch <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1\"><math alttext=\"1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span> open and Switch <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn></math></span></span> closed</p>",
        "value": "i3"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">There is no combination of switch positions that results in Bulb <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1\"><math alttext=\"1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span> being off and Bulb <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2\"><math alttext=\"2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn></math></span></span> being on.</p>",
        "value": "i4"
      }
    ]
